short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Look up trends for the selected text with Google Trends

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Select any text to look up trends for it with just two clicks: right click to call the context menu and then choose "Look up trends for ..." to open Google Trends in a new tab.

Configure your default lookup preferences, such as location country and time/date, in the extension settings.
